I"d<p>Vis À Vis is a <strong>3D first-person atmospheric horror</strong> game. It was built for <a href="https://itch.io/jam/extra-credits-game-jam-4">Extra Credits Game Jam #4</a>. The player has to escape the world of mirrors they find themselves trapped in.</p>

<p>The game was built using <strong>Unreal Engine 4</strong> and written in <strong>C++</strong> and <strong>Blueprints</strong>. I worked in a team of four on this, as a <strong>gameplay programmer</strong>. I was responsible for most of the other programming related functionalities, such as <strong>the UI</strong>, as well.</p>

<p>It is my most popular game so far, with 2600+ views, 800+ downloads and in 90+ collections on itch.io. Here’s a gameplay video:</p>

